member.remarks:
If you specify an object to be invisible, it will be invisible regardless of the application 
visible setting. Other factors can also cause an object to be invisible; 
for example, an object will not be displayed if its layer is off or frozen.

member.value:
true if arrowhead blocks set by  and 
shall be used;
false if arrowhead block set by  shall be used.

member.summary:
Execute a method in a time span if the method don't finish at the time is canceled.
Example:
    Action method = () => TaskExample(10);
    bool test = TaskManager.ExecuteWithTimeLimit(3000, method);
    if the action isn't finish in 3 seconds will stop the execution and return false.
